library(tidymodels)
library(gapminder)

  head()

gapminder %>% 
  filter(year == 2007) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = log(gdpPercap), 
             y = lifeExp, 
             group = continent,
             color = continent)) + 
  geom_point() + 
  geom_smooth(method = lm, se = FALSE) + 
  scale_color_viridis_d()

lm_model <- linear_reg() %>% 
  set_engine("lm")

lm_fit <- lm_model %>% 
  fit(lifeExp ~ log(gdpPercap) + year + continent, data = gapminder)

lm_fit %>% tidy()

continentOceania 12.7507191 1.2747630 10.00242 0 
new_data <- tibble(gdpPercap = 50000,
                   year = 2007,
                   continent = c("Africa", "Americas", "Asia", "Europe", "Oceania"))

mean_pred <- predict(lm_fit, new_data = new_data)
ci_pred <- predict(lm_fit, new_data = new_data, type = "conf_int")

new_data %>% 
  bind_cols(mean_pred) %>% 
  bind_cols(ci_pred) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = continent)) + 
  geom_point(aes(y = .pred)) + 
  geom_errorbar(aes(ymin = .pred_lower,
                    ymax = .pred_upper),
                width = 0.2) + 
  labs(y = "lifeExp")
